# Todo Skill

Use the managed weeknotes handler for todo operations.

## Input Contract

User input is everything after `/todo`.

- `add <text...>`: add a todo entry.
- `list`: list open todos.
- `reminder`: internal reminder output used by scheduler.

## Execution Rules

Always execute exactly one command:

```bash
/home/node/.openclaw/skills/{{ openclaw_weeknotes_skill_name }}/handler.sh todo <raw-user-input>
```

When no input is provided, return:

`Usage: /todo add <text> | /todo list`

Return the handler output as-is.
